{"tid":2053514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連加特：普巴係曼聯領袖","createTime":"2020-06-06T10:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T10:54:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b98f8c5c49ad4b200684348ae3e78bc83669c881","tid":2053514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】雖然普巴常被批評自私，但曼聯隊友連加特仍然認為對方是領袖的材料。<br />\n<br />\n普巴（Paul Pogba）在2016年夏天以當時最高轉會費8900萬鎊，從祖雲達斯回歸曼聯，被認為將會成為領袖，帶領紅魔重返高峰。可惜，他未能踢出身價，表現受炮轟之餘亦有離心。<br />\n<br />\n從小便於青年軍合作的連加特（Jesse Lingard）說：「我跟普巴一起成長。很年輕的時候，你已經看到你的技術有多出色。現在，他贏得世界盃等多個冠軍，成為了非常全面、完整的球員。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然普巴不時被攻擊自我及沒有責任心，但連加特認為：「他十分謙虛，而且經常於更衣室保持正面，鼓勵失意的隊友。他已經負上了很多責任，成為了球隊的領袖。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"37bd77fe1e1a19561c81bc219cacc400f83cdf76","tid":2053514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/30a5606982a9074351cc68945c851a06/tenor.gif?itemid=10416684\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F30a5606982a9074351cc68945c851a06%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D10416684&h=18abcc26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b59863d1c8c548eaca98d2e38f1fdc539fb32d8","tid":2053514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.daznservices.com/di/library/goal_uk/c3/3f/jesse-lingard-paul-pogba-man-utd-premier-league_eqt1u3epwqyl1odpzvkkv2tst.jpg?t=1728808783&amp;quality=60&amp;w=1200&amp;h=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.daznservices.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2Fgoal_uk%2Fc3%2F3f%2Fjesse-lingard-paul-pogba-man-utd-premier-league_eqt1u3epwqyl1odpzvkkv2tst.jpg%3Ft%3D1728808783%26quality%3D60%26w%3D1200%26h%3D800&h=67942272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cf85aecfcff516bad0b486f86d447f3b68c8f1f","tid":2053514,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"佢似係真係天生領袖而唔係爭住做嗰種"}]}